| 1914 | United States | [Ireland a Nation](/Ireland_a_Nation) | | Walter MacNamara | A historical drama focusing on the [Irish Rebellion of 1798](/Irish_Rebellion_of_1798), an event inextricably linked to the broader upheaval of the [French Revolutionary Wars](/French_Revolutionary_Wars) as the French sought to destabilize British rule. It’s a reminder that revolutionary fervor wasn't confined to the continent. |
